title: John Holdsworth (rugby union)
text:
John Wynne Holdsworth (born 10 September 1884) was a <a href="rugby%20union">rugby union</a> player who represented Australia.
Holdsworth, a <a href="Lock%20%28rugby%20union%29">lock</a>, was born in Sydney and claimed a total of 6 international rugby caps for Australia.
